#

Loaded Mashed Potato Casserole with Bacon and Cheese

45 min
$10
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

MainSide

Tags:

comfort foodcasseroleeasybaconcheese

Description

Creamy mashed potatoes loaded with crispy bacon and gooey cheese, baked to perfection.

Ingredients

  • mashed potatoes: 4 cups
  • bacon: 6 slices
  • cheddar cheese: 2 cups
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • green onions: 1/2 cup
  • butter: 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
